{"tid":1375722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CLS申請元朗不反對通知書失敗個鐘建平比警狗拉左！","createTime":"2019-07-28T06:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T07:20:31.000Z","uid":14503,"like":106,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bcce8a53d86425ea55a91986f5bdec2bf1731f09","tid":1375722,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"CLS架咁都入鐘建平數，咁以後真係唔撚洗申請不反了，有申請過不反就入佢數，死警狗搵人祭旗製造白色恐怖！"},{"pid":"40a61a8324aaf70364c9b8ad0a67e1390467bff5","tid":1375722,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"529bfda7dccc48a12a0db9b9b894c5391e2d6d06","tid":1375722,"uid":14503,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"市民：我要出嚟遊行反對你林鄭月娥唔聽市民意見！！<br />\n市民：請問林鄭媽媽批唔批准？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥：唔批准！我唔想聽唔想見唔想理，你出嚟我就搵警察拉你！<br />\n市民：喔，咁冇事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥：乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民：我要出嚟遊行反對你班黑警濫用暴力打市民同埋亂咁拉人！！<br />\n市民：請問阿Sir哥哥批唔批准？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警：唔批准！你一出黎我就打鳩你拉鳩你！<br />\n市民：喔，咁冇事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警：乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><br />\n玩完啦收工喇，場運動完左喇！<br />\n<br />\n你係咪想咁？<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係乜撚嘢邏輯？<br />\n<br />\n好明顯係家長式管治，你仲buy??? </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家你行出嚟係為咗反對政府反對黑警，咁你係咪要等政府同黑警批准你行出嚟你先行？如果係嘅話咁乜撚嘢都唔使做啦！<br />\n<br />\n佢批唔批不反對通知書根本唔應該係你出唔出嚟行既考慮因素，你依家係反對政府反對黑警你返而同佢申請根本就係與虎謀皮，係冇可能既，係矛盾行為！你要反對佢你就行出黎就係咁簡單！<br />\n<br />\n如果有一次冇不反對通知書嘅情況下都有100萬人出黎行既話我哋就會勝利，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地要用民意推翻不反對通知書呢個矛盾制度！！！<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3c1a1937f292e248d17051df8f22e1767231d0ff","tid":1375722,"uid":199727,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老老實實<br />\n根本佢有無申請<br />\n我地都係照入元朗買老婆餅"},{"pid":"cc5544d66408d43cbe4fae6e2cf43dbf1fcd6008","tid":1375722,"uid":63154,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"反效果，本來呢個角色有知會一聲嘅作用，以後連呢一個角色都冇埋"},{"pid":"2fd7c2041ca61d12ad725b038ebbc3a4ea6d630e","tid":1375722,"uid":14503,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cc5544d66408d43cbe4fae6e2cf43dbf1fcd6008","tid":1375722,"uid":63154,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"反效果，本來呢個角色有知會一聲嘅作用，以後連呢一個角色都冇埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"警犬真係逆智商"},{"pid":"c747d5bc0df7901d9cad06872afb9b3fa7c40fee","tid":1375722,"uid":11034,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"又靠嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一早喺新聞度講咗唔呼籲人哋去遊行啦！<br />\n<br />\n根本冇證據， 就搵佢祭旗"},{"pid":"adac4ae736cd88f42956f3be35bb6badfaf6d4d4","tid":1375722,"uid":14503,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c747d5bc0df7901d9cad06872afb9b3fa7c40fee","tid":1375722,"uid":11034,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"又靠嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一早喺新聞度講咗唔呼籲人哋去遊行啦！<br />\n<br />\n根本冇證據， 就搵佢祭旗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"做比市民睇嚇鳩d市民囉，志在製造白色恐怖"},{"pid":"b86393df3013b64c49ca5290b75d751beeae8a41","tid":1375722,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77fb44a45b5ba8ac8214be4b613